1981 NOVEMBER 25<br>
<br>
SANTO, RANDALL.<br>
<br>
City Police searched the shoreline near Gig Harbor Thursday for
the body of an apparent suicide victim who jumped off the Narrows Bridge Tuesday.  Santo has had a history of suicidal tendencies said his ex-girl friend who was allegedly raped by Santo before he was seen "running around" on the bridge. When police arrived at the Tacoma Narrows Bridge "..Santo jumped over the railing. His body was last seen floating motionless southwest. (Tacoma News Tribune November 25, 1981.).<br>
