<h1>Tacoma Street Car Crash of 1900</h1>
<p>Enter a new <A HREF="http://www.tpl.lib.wa.us/nwr/unsetng.htm">Unsettling Events search</A>, Return to the <A HREF="http://www.tpl.lib.wa.us/nwr/nwhome.htm">NWR Home Page</A> or Return to the <A HREF="http://www.tpl.lib.wa.us">Tacoma Public Library Home Page</A>
<hr>
<br>
STREET CAR LINES.<br>
<br>
1908.<br>
<br>
A. Pacific Traction Company. 917 Pacific Avenue.<br>
<br>
J.R. Thompson, President. E.J. Felt, Vice President and Treasurer.<br>
<br>
Routes:<br>
<br>
1. From 9th and Commerce, via Cliff Avenue N. 2nd .<br>
<br>
2. Division and Sprague Avenues to Tacoma Baseball Athletic Association Grounds at South 15th and Sprague thence via Oakland Addition to American Lake and Steilacocom Asylum.<br>
<br>
3. From South 54th Street and Union Avenue (South Tacoma) to American Lake and Steilacoom Asylum.<br>
<br>
B. Puget Sound Electric Railway<br>
<br>
Jacob Furth (Seattle), President; W.S. Dimmock, (Tacoma), Manger. General Offices 1319 A Street. Freight and Passenger Station South 8th, nw corner of A.<br>
<br>
C. Tacoma Railway and Power Company.<br>
<br>
Office, Barn and Power House, A. Foot of South 13th Streets.<br>
<br>
W.S. Dimmock, Manager; A.W. Q. Birtwell, Assistant Treasurer; F.A. Boutelle, Superintendent.<br>
<br>
1. Cable line from A to K on South llth, returning on South 13th to A.<br>
<br>
2. Electric Lines. Pacific Avenue from Ocean Wharf to South 34th.<br>
<br>
3. Puyallup Avenue and East 25th to East P. and 35th.<br>
<br>
4. St. Helens and North Tacoma Avenues to Old Town.<br>
<br>
5. Sixth avenue to Glendale.<br>
<br>
6. North 12th and Pine via North O and K to South 23rd and Sprague avenue.<br>
<br>
7. K and South llth to Steilacoom.<br>
<br>
8. South 9th and Commerce, via Jefferson Avenue and Center to
Sprague Avenue.<br>
<br>
9.  South 17th and C Streets to Tacoma Smelter and Point Defiance.<br>
<br>
10. Ocean Wharf to South Tacoma and American Lake.<br>
<br>
11. South 7th and Pacific to Puyallup  and Spanaway Lake via Fern Hill.<br>
<br>
12. Ocean Wharf to McKinley Park Addition via Pacific and Puyallup Avenues.<br>
<br>
13. East D, East E and East H to East 37th Streets.<br>
<br>
14. Tide flats via South 11th, St. Paul Avenue and Canal Street.<br>
