Little pictures and personality profiles of all the engines on
the Island of Sodor.
</UL>

<P>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.public.iastate.edu/~jmilne/pooh.html">Page at Pooh Corner</a> <BR>
Fans of Winnie the Pooh will find trivia, author and illustrator
info, and even song lyrics.
</UL>

<P>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.pbs.org:80/readingrainbow/rrlist.html">Reading Rainbow Home Page</a> <BR>
