<LI><A HREF="http://www.kidlink.org:80/home-std.html">Kidlink</a><BR>
For kids age 10-15, a global dialog. Kids from 80 countries participate.
Not only interesting for outlook, but great practice for foreign
languages.
<LI><A HREF="http://funnelweb.utcc.utk.edu/~etsulliv/medieval.html">Medieval World</a><BR>
Link goldmine for Arthurian lit, medieval customs, food, architecture,
folklore, crusades, knights, etc.
