<PRE>
Search on Ship Names and Shipping Topics: <SELECT NAME="searchby" SIZE=5><OPTION SELECTED>1. Starting With<OPTION>2. Containing (slow search)<OPTION>3. Exactly like<OPTION>4. Sounding Like<OPTION>5. Description containing (SLOWEST! search)</SELECT>
