<H5>To apply for the position of Library Director the applicant
must submit:</H5>

<UL>
<LI>Letter of application;
<LI>Resume;
<LI>Salary history;
<LI>Three professional references.
</UL>

<H5>All application materials must be received or postmarked by
5:00 P.M., August 2, 1996.</H5>

<P>
All application materials are to be mailed to:
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<I>Lee T. Pasquarella<BR>
Jensen, Oldani, &amp; Cooper, Inc.<BR>
411 108th Avenue NE, Suite 250<BR>
Bellevue, Washington 98004<BR>
Phone: (206) 451-3938<BR>
Fascimile: (206) 453-6786</I>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

<H4><A HREF="#topofpage">Return to top of page</H4></a>
