<A NAME="process"></A><H3>Recruitment &amp; selection process:</H3>

<P>
1. All resumes will be reviewed by <I>Jensen, Oldani, &amp; Cooper,
Inc.</I> <BR>
Top applicants for the position will be invited to submit a Tacoma
Public Library application package <BR>
and Supplemental Questionnaire
<P>
2. Selected candidates will be interviewed in Tacoma, Washington
by the Library's Board of Trustees, <BR>
Library staff and the community.
<H3>Recruitment schedule:</H3>

<UL>
