</B>Opening date for all applications.
<LI><B>August 2 <BR>
</B>Closing date for all applications.
<LI><B>June 30 - August 2 <BR>
</B>Initial screening of applications. <BR>
Top candidates selected by consultant for further consideration.
<LI><B>August 8 - 25 <BR>
</B>Consultant researches and interviews top candidates, and checks
references. <BR>
Final candidates are recommended to the Tacoma Public Library's
Board of Trustees <BR>
for final consideration.
<LI><B>September 9 - 19 <BR>
</B>Library Trustees interview final candidates in Tacoma, Washington
<LI><B>October 17 <BR>
</B>Library Director is selected
</UL>

