<TR><TD></TD><TD><A HREF="/oct/food/basictoc.html"><IMG BORDER=0  SRC="http://www.entermag.com/august/food/basic.jpeg" ALT="Back to Basics"></A></TD><TD WIDTH=5></TD><TD><A HREF="http://www.entermag.com/"><IMG BORDER=0  SRC="/oct/tocart/logo3.gif"></A>
